query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('debian',
'ffmpeg',
'grammatical-number',
'laptop',
'line-breaking',
'listings',
'lists',
'luatex',
'meaning-in-context',
'multiple-monitors',
'packages',
'pdftex',
'punctuation',
'synonyms',
'windows-vista')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('english',
'superuser',
'tex')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000 group by t1.name;
